    "problemStatement": "Given an array AAA of length NNN, you have to perform QQQ queries on it.\n\nThere are three different type of queries:\n\n\n111 LLL RRR - For every iii such that L\u2264i\u2264RL \\le i \\le RL\u2264i\u2264R and Ai&gt;0A_i \\gt 0Ai\u200b&gt;0, replace AiA_iAi\u200b with AiA_iAi\u200b \u2223|\u2223 (Ai\u22121)(A_i-1)(Ai\u200b\u22121).\n222 LLL RRR - For every iii such that L\u2264i\u2264RL \\le i \\le RL\u2264i\u2264R and Ai&gt;0A_i \\gt 0Ai\u200b&gt;0, replace AiA_iAi\u200b with AiA_iAi\u200b &amp;\\&amp;&amp; (Ai\u22121)(A_i-1)(Ai\u200b\u22121).\n333 xxx - Print AxA_xAx\u200b.\nOutput the answer to each query of type 333.\n\n\nInput Format\n\nThe first line contains 222 integers, NNN and QQQ - the number of elements in the array AAA and the number of queries, respectively.\nThe next line contains NNN integers - A1A_1A1\u200b, A2A_2A2\u200b, \u2026\\ldots\u2026, ANA_NAN\u200b, the elements of the array AAA.\niii-th line of the next QQQ lines contains the description of the iii-th query.\n\n\nOutput Format\nFor each query of type 333, output the value of AxA_xAx\u200b.",
    "constraints": [
      "1\u2264N\u22642\u00d71051 \\le N \\le 2\\times10^51\u2264N\u22642\u00d7105",
      "1\u2264Q\u22643\u00d71051 \\le Q \\le 3\\times10^51\u2264Q\u22643\u00d7105",
      "0\u2264Ai\u2264230\u221210 \\le A_i \\le 2^{30}-10\u2264Ai\u200b\u2264230\u22121",
      "For queries of type 111 and 222, 1\u2264L\u2264R\u2264N1 \\le L \\le R \\le N1\u2264L\u2264R\u2264N",
      "For queries of type 333, 1\u2264x\u2264N1 \\le x \\le N1\u2264x\u2264N"
    ],
